      "span_text": "An ASFV gene with similarity to the ERV1 (essential for respiration and viability) gene family [CITATION_1] has been identified in the pathogenic ASFV isolate Malawi Lil-20/1 (ORF, 9GL) and a cell culture-adapted European virus, BA71V (ORF, pB119L) (65; Lu et al., unpublished data)."
